Battera::

She flew high enough to stay out of most scanners, but might be 
picked up on radar.  She flew lower and started to circle down 
towards Hydras' base. She landed near the edge of thier territory. 
She transformed intobot mode and started to walk into thier zone. 
Anytime now, she would be picked up by thier sensors and  she would 
have to be ready. She pulled her plasma pistol and walked with it at 
her side, ready.
